Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:16.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:20.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a bit too far from the foothold to go back to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:24.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I need to come up with a way to bring her to a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:27.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:28.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:29.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:32.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rico! Eclair!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:34.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for running late, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:36.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:32.63,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(600,505)\pos(178,353)}  「Flying Flower In The Night」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:35.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair, I'm glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:38.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Didn't I say that I'd be back soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:39.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rico too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:41.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:46.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,While I was on my way here, I saw Eclair falling from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we were reunited.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:51.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And when we heard that the two of you were in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:56.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haran, we're about to arrive! Give it all you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:14.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the thing that startled \Nour young princess and Sir Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:20.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect them to get rid of the demon that had been possessed by this evil sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:23.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:28.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that the princess and Sink could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:34.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, time for us to get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon this fleeting life, I hold this blade of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:52.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is our duty to seal it for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:54.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand miles across the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:59.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Revolving for several hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:02.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the fox spirit land god, Yukikaze,{high ranking kitsune (fox spirit)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:04.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the master swordsman of exorcism, d'Arquien!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:10.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With the flow circulated from our travels,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:14.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the five hundred and nine sealed calamity blades...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no room for evil in heaven or on earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon you, Calamity Blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:33.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Flashing Fangs of the Divine Wolf,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:35.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,seal the demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:07.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we done?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:12.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my lady! It's been captured within the sealing knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:22.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be reported to the princess and everyone else waiting at the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll go right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:32.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Omitsu Squad, those who intend to tag along can come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:43.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that is its mother, who begged me to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:46.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I heard about the evil sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:50.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellead and Palladion had shared their power with us up 'til now.{Apostrophe goes at the beginning of "til" as it replaces "un" in "until".}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:59.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, this just goes to show that you did well yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:02.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Most demons are cursed and thus receive a pitiful fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:08.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you did not just kill the demon, but you also helped my kind in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:11.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I couldn't have done it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:14.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all thanks to Sink and Princess Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:19.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You also did very well! I must give you a good petting later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:21.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:28.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Yukikaze, is it true that its mother has already...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:35.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The mother that you met was swallowed by the demon's flesh and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:40.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe she has already become one with her child spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:45.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the demon's body has been destroyed, and the child has been saved,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:48.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe the mother's spirit has returned to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:57.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, would you let me take care of this little fox?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:59.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:04.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of it from home until it recovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:05.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is Princess Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:12.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully her injuries aren't too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:18.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About the guards of the castle, and Biscotti's Team Two,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:23.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there were some who suffered injuries, but none died or went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:28.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As the face of the demon was broadcast, all fights were put to a halt.{"broadcasted" is less proper than "broadcast" as the past tense}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:34.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The citizens of both countries worried for Princess Leo and Princess Millhi's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:36.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:42.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up the hall and tell the media that I would like to make an announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:45.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:51.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An immediate announcement took place for the citizens of Biscotti and Galette who had been worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:59.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The announcement recited Princess Leo's apology and the reason the war was put to a halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:02.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason was that a huge demon appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:05.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and casualties occurred as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:10.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She thus announced an investigation into why the demon had appeared while ensuring the safely of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:13.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we're still not sure why the demon showed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:16.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in over my head this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:21.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably divine judgment for putting our country's Holy Swords up as a bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:27.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For ending the war that everyone have been expecting just like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:33.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as the organizing party, I sincerely apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:38.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, we'll organize a more enjoyable war unlike this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:43.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we will consult Biscotti first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:46.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a leader, upon experiencing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:49.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to further improve myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:52.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I haven't been the most reliable leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:57.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will everyone in Galette continue to support me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:03.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will everyone in Biscotti participate in the wars that I'll organize?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:20.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,3000)}And that was Princess Leo's apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:22.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, on that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:25.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to make up for discontinuing the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:29.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a last-minute concert by the princess was organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:37.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, you need to move to this position according to the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:38.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:43.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero, Eclair has briefed me about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:47.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. It's because of you that everything went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:51.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I need to apologize for getting Eclair injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:54.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't. She's a knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:56.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is nothing you should be worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:58.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, she was wounded gloriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:02.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I used to see Flonyard as a peaceful country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:05.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there are demons like that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:06.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:10.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also my first time seeing such a huge demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:12.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you should have heard
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:17.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that the minute we step out of the protected area, we'll definitely encounter danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:19.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore the wars that we normally have
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:26.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,exist so that the people remember that they need to keep their fighting spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:27.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:30.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's not good to wave around power that could hurt people,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:36.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,once we give up on fighting, we won't be able to protect things important to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:38.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:40.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:44.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:47.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The staff would like to discuss the concert security with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:49.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:53.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll see you later, Sir Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:54.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:04.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for you to walk around?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:06.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:13.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, have you eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:17.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a stall over there. Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:21.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Great idea! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:27.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What interesting progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:28.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:36.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:38.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:40.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:41.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cocona Pucca.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:44.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Injured people can eat it, and it's nutritious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:47.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:52.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cocona Pucca?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:59.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Eclair actually asked a guy to eat with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:02.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ricotta is superbly touched!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:03.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:06.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The atmosphere is rather good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:11.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:16.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have saved the princess on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:24.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As the captain of the knights of Biscotti, I would like to salute you for your courage and spirit to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You honor me, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:37.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it were you, just there on your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:39.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you would've done something,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:45.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because you're the captain who was \Nprotecting the princess before I arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:52.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, just like that, just a bit more... gush!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gush!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:58.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:01.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are the two of you up to hiding here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:03.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, ear-drooping doggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:06.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Gaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:15.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you guys sure were awesome back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:16.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.74,0:13:19.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a lot of stuff happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:22.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, as soon as the demon was defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:26.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,my sister seemed to be less energetic,\Nas if she had lost something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:31.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't tell me the whole story then, but she said she'd tell me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:32.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:36.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I've heard from Bernard,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:39.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the extra activity for war will continue as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:44.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the war has ended. All the messy stuff has been taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The demon has been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:52.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that Biscotti and Galette have regained peace again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:54.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:56.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:14:01.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The results were still satisfying even though the war ended only half finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:04.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's really great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:10.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:15.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rico, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:26.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The people at the Research Institute want me to get in touch with them immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:30.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero, Prince Gaul,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:33.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall make a move first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:34.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:36.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:40.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The decoration of the stage is almost completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:42.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the lighting is being tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:45.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:53.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:15:00.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for coming at such a busy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:05.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really did something bad this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:07.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:13.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I put you in danger, and I wasted the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll officially apologize soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:20.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I was tough on you this past half year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:29.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The days of war and what happened today have taught me a lot of important things as a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:32.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've learned to prepare for war and danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:36.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to protect the people, and to realize the \Ndifficulty and importance of guiding the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:45.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I can sincerely swear from my heart to become a much better leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:49.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I've got you to thank, Princess Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:57.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Most importantly, after hearing what you did all this while was all for my well-being...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:16:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, who did you hear that from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Biore and Rouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:04.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:06.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't blame them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:08.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I forced them to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:16.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell you this myself. That's why I \Nasked you out right before your performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:19.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:25.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know, I was really happy when I heard about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:28.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but right now I am a bit mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You once said, "The future lies in our own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:38.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Being threatened by fortune telling or star reading is pure foolishness!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:41.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mindset remains the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:44.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You say so, but you were still worried about the star reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:49.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You hid the truth from me and protected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:57.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you always took care of me when I was younger,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:17:00.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,700)}I have grown up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:03.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have trustworthy subordinates and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:10.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Princess Leo, you do not have to sacrifice yourself to protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:13.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:18.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You kept protecting me and loving me when we were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:24.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how much warmth you supported me with?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:29.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to disappear, if I were to be in a world without you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:36.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Princess Leo. I won't disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:44.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leo is a renowned and \Nexcellent leader, but she's still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:48.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps our concern wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:49.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:55.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We still need the Leader of the Knights to \Ndiscreetly keep in touch with General Bernard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:59.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It'd be great if you could be of help as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:06.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been some time since you saw the embarrassing side of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:08.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't embarrassing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:13.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, we're really sorry, but it's time for the rehearsal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:12.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:16.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I took so much of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:17.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I heard your last song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:22.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have the honor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:26.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I'll sing my best!
