Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:23.72,Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\blur10}I'll run with you 'til the faraway end
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:29.19,Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\blur10\fs40}I'll hold your hands and move, I'll grab them tightly and never let them go
