Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:59.55,Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\blur10\fs40}Hide tiny bits of courage within our hearts and coagulate wishes deep in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:05.24,Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\blur10\fs40}Even now, no matter when it is, I'll believe in continuously moving forward
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:10.66,Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\blur10}I'll pass on words overflowing with longing feelings
