Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:46.45,Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\blur10}Our miraculous encounter is right under this starry sky
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:51.87,Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\blur10\fs40}It'll become a gentle bond, and we'll softly harmonize with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:57.56,Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\blur10}When our eyes meet, and our hearts are in agreement
